Space Invaders Prefab

Made by The Giblets of Jesus


This prefab consists of 32 static, dev textured space invaders that explode and release gibs in random directions when shot with any weapon. Each invader killed also adds to a score, represented on a scoreboard that can be reset by pressing the reset button or restarting the round. The other button, as seen in the video below, will spawn all the invaders in turn.

Demo videos






If you do decide to use this prefab in one of your maps, I'd like to be credited as appropriate, it'd be nice to told as well.
